Note on Installing the system on a new machine.

First up we need apache and mysql setup, using Ubuntu this is simple enough.
More notes here as I do it.

Perl Things To Install Using CPAN
Plack
Moose
Mojolicious
MooseX::Storage
JSON::Any

Link the src folder 
ln -s /home/simon/src/wargames /var/wargames
ln -s /home/simon/src/wargames/RESOURCES/local-apache.conf /etc/apache2/sites-available/wargames

Add wargames.localhost to /etc/hosts

The .htaccess is expecting a password in httpauth.... removing for local development